<plot>Work in a factory is monotonous. For humans, but also for robots. One of those sentient robotic arms looks away. He doesn't respond when the to be constructed machinery passes by. He's dreaming of other places. Even an alerting knock of one of his fellow robots, isn't enough to get him back to work. Too late, there's the superintendent. Quickly the superintendent replaces the daydreaming robot and throws him to the trash pile. This looks like the ultimate chance to escape.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?078298</url></doc>
